{"tid":1602861,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"手足們 你地係咪寧願會屈錯前線既風險都要捉鬼？","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:04:59.000Z","uid":83627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"279cf691786eacb280cf3aa4878b65ff636cefd2","tid":1602861,"uid":83627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"利申 全部聽返黎<br />\n<br />\n今日係老銅出少少 企咗10分鐘就見到兩批前線服裝有綠帶既 俾人話係鬼 兩次都有成十幾人跟住佢地一路行一路鬧<br />\n前一批既一個男仔除低個面罩鬧返轉頭 話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係前面幫你地頂 你地係度話我地係鬼？！</span></span><br />\n第二批有個女仔直接除低面罩喊住咁話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁我除低俾你影lo</span></span><br />\n你地諗下 佢地由老銅行到金鐘 俾幾百人輪流鬧既滋味<br />\n<br />\n其實個陣我都唔知佢地會唔會係鬼<br />\n但係我知前線已經冒住好大風險<br />\n佢地已經要驚俾狗打 俾狗射<br />\n甚至係聽過新屋領幾恐怖下 佢地一樣出黎<br />\n可唔可以唔好再要佢地驚俾人當鬼？"},{"pid":"bc42d5de07cc2f689052730d22bf5961e313f6cc","tid":1602861,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d859cf6da950ff6dd7f9ec1c83f73152d1de4141","tid":1602861,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edb671db7c9d36c2b0f7d5aa3d06345c204337f4","tid":1602861,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"模下條腰 同小腿 有無<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">槍 </span>咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7898f0444c6b183c3aaab1dc86c9e6f42fe0291","tid":1602861,"uid":271354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"最撚癲係show 學生證 身分證都信唔過<br />\n唔該大家真係咪撚再咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df89cf2bd5c67443b77eb65bd9926669b71be35","tid":1602861,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco